item.title: Frequently asked questions
item.description: How to migrate data from CVAT.org to CVAT.ai Please follow the export tasks and projects guide to download an archive with data which corresponds to your task or project. The backup for a project will have all tasks which are inside the project. Thus you don’t need to export them separately. Please follow the import tasks and projects guide to upload your backup with a task or project to a CVAT instance.
